I see him every now and then.

495
00:33:38,110 --> 00:33:40,210
It looks like he really hit it big.

496
00:33:40,210 --> 00:33:43,180
Hit it big, my foot. He was just lucky.

497
00:33:44,060 --> 00:33:49,930
I guess. Honestly, I always thought you would be big like Yeong Jae is now.

498
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:53,770
I thought he would be living precariously like you are now.

499
00:33:53,810 --> 00:33:56,290
But it's the total opposite.

500
00:33:57,130 --> 00:33:59,690
Should I take the food back?

501
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:08,980
Anyway, I really want to see him. There's something I need to ask him, too.

502
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:11,210
Do you think you could pull some strings?

503
00:34:11,210 --> 00:34:14,690
Forget it. I told you not to cause any trouble.

504
00:34:14,690 --> 00:34:17,140
Trouble?

505
00:34:17,140 --> 00:34:20,500
Also, is there something I can't eat?

506
00:34:20,500 --> 00:34:22,630
What?
- A food I can't eat.

507
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,090
You should know that. How would I know?

508
00:34:24,090 --> 00:34:26,630
- You were my manager.
- Well, I don't know.

509
00:34:26,630 --> 00:34:29,570
Hey, from now one, don't call me up just to talk about this kind of stuff.

510
00:34:29,570 --> 00:34:33,230
I'm busy enough without you interfering.

511
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:35,600
Is someone in there?

512
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:38,290
Damn it.

513
00:34:43,260 --> 00:34:44,760
You can't hide together with me.

514
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,280
Hey, pick one. Hide or don't hide?

515
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:47,750
- You hide.
- No, you hide.

516
00:34:47,750 --> 00:34:50,870
Get in there.

517
00:34:56,910 --> 00:35:00,600
That's strange. I definitely heard someone talking.

518
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:02,970
What's this bread doing here?

519
00:35:07,260 --> 00:35:09,240
Oh, man.

520
00:35:10,090 --> 00:35:13,560
Hey, look what you got me into.

521
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:16,790
It would've been fine if you hadn't hid.

522
00:35:16,790 --> 00:35:19,140
I need to pee.

523
00:35:21,260 --> 00:35:22,500
Hold it.

524
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:24,750
I can't.

525
00:35:24,750 --> 00:35:30,800
You're just like the building owner. Completely useless.

526
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:33,870
- It's too cramped.
- Don't touch me!

527
00:35:33,870 --> 00:35:36,920
There's no space.

528
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:02,570
The Best Hit

529
00:36:02,570 --> 00:36:04,330
♫ The stars floating in the night sky ♫
